@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "FastAPI API" as API
participant "Auth Service" as AUTH
database "SQLite" as DB

User -> FE : Вводит логин и пароль
FE -> API : POST /api/auth/login
API -> AUTH : verify_credentials()
AUTH -> DB : SELECT user by username
DB --> AUTH : user record
AUTH -> AUTH : verify password hash
AUTH -> DB : INSERT session token
DB --> AUTH : session saved
AUTH --> API : token + user profile
API --> FE : 200 OK
FE --> User : Отображение панели по роли
@enduml
